Text: FW HeyOriginal Message From mailto Sent Monday October PM To Subject Hey Hey there So are we all ready for Halloween Mikey and Marissa cant wait Weve had some practice already with the town parade and a few parties I thought they would sleep in the darn costumes Mikey is Batman and Marissa is Pooh Bear How are the girls Is Pete watching the ball games Mike cant stand it Hes driving me crazy with his sour moods Will anyone be visiting you for Thanksgiving What are your plans for Christmas I hope we can get together this time around I cant wait to see little Caroline Bob Spear just had another girl He names her Caroline also Well back to the rugrats Johanna
